'''西西莉·泰森'''（{{lang-en|Cicely Tyson}}；{{bd|1924年|12月19日|2021年|1月28日|catIdx=Tyson}}）是美国女演员和模特儿。

==生平==
1924年12月19日，西西莉·泰森出生在[[纽约市|纽约市]][[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]][[哈莱姆|哈莱姆]]，<ref name="ancestry">{{cite web|title=New York, Naturalization Records, 1882-1944 (database online)|url=http://search.ancestry.com/search/db.aspx?dbid=2499|publisher=Ancestry.com. Original source: The National Archives and Records Administration (NARA), Washington, D.C.; Petitions for Naturalization from the U.S. District Court for the Southern District of New York, 1897-1944; Series M1972, Roll 956|access-date=2021-01-29|ref=In the matter of the petition of William Augustine Tyson to be admitted to become a citizen of the United States of America, Petition No. 248743 (S.D.N.Y., Jul. 31, 1935; granted January 27, 1936)|archive-date=2018-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181029030847/https://search.ancestry.com/search/db.aspx?dbid=2499|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Cicely Tyson Biography|url=http://www.biography.com/people/cicely-tyson-9512950|publisher=biography.com|access-date=February 17, 2015|archive-date=2019-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413122615/https://www.biography.com/people/cicely-tyson-9512950|dead-url=no}}</ref>母亲弗雷德里卡（哈金斯）泰森是一名家庭佣工；父亲威廉·奥古斯丁·泰森曾是一名木匠、画家，以及做其他工作。她是家里的三个孩子之一。<ref>{{Cite web|last=CNN|first=Anika Myers Palm|title=Cicely Tyson, iconic and influential actress, dies at 96|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/28/entertainment/cicely-tyson-obit/index.html|access-date=2021-01-29|website=CNN|archive-date=2021-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210504212845/https://www.cnn.com/2021/01/28/entertainment/cicely-tyson-obit/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她的父母是[[西印度群岛|西印度群岛]][[尼维斯岛|尼维斯岛]]的移民。<ref>[http://www.filmreference.com/film/3/Cicely-Tyson.html Cicely Tyson profile] {{Wayback|url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/3/Cicely-Tyson.html |date=20170624002341 }}, Filmreference.com; retrieved 2013-08-09.</ref><ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20121106104318/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-67858566.html CICELY TYSON: BAH, HUMBUG? ACTRESS STARS AS MS. SCROOGE.(LIVING)]. ''The Cincinnati Post'', November 28, 1997.</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1972/10/01/archives/cicely-the-looker-from-sounder-cicely-the-looker.html|work=The New York Times|title=Cicely, the Looker From 'Sounder'; Cicely, the Looker|date=1972-10-01|access-date=2021-01-29|first=Judy|last=Klemesrud|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029220335/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F70612F73C5A137A93C3A9178BD95F468785F9|dead-url=no}}</ref>她的父亲在21岁时来到纽约市，并于1919年8月4日在[[埃利斯岛|埃利斯岛]]接受体检。<ref>[http://www.ellisisland.org/search/passRecord.asp?pID=603815010445 The Staue of Liberty – Ellis Island Foundation, Inc] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ellisisland.org/search/passRecord.asp?pID=603815010445 |date=20200225070237 }}, Ellisisland.org; retrieved 2013-08-09.</ref>

==家庭==
1942年12月27日，18岁的泰森和肯尼思·富兰克林结婚。<ref>{{cite web |title=Marriage License |url=https://search.ancestry.com/cgi-bin/sse.dll?dbid=61788&h=90384728&indiv=try&o_vc=Record:OtherRecord&rhSource=2442 |website=Ancestry |publisher=New York City Department of Records & Information Services |access-date=2021-01-29}}</ref>她丈夫在结婚不到18个月就抛弃了她，1956年，法院正式解除这段婚姻。

20世纪60年代，泰森第一次和爵士小号手[[比利·迪·威廉斯|比利·迪·威廉斯]]约会，当时他正在和舞蹈家弗朗西斯·泰勒·戴维斯闹离婚。<ref>{{Cite journal|date=February 15, 1968|title=Miles Davis And Wife Now 'Miles Apart'|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=LrgDAAAAMBAJ&q=cicely+tyson+miles+davis+jet+1968&pg=PA23|journal=Jet|volume=33|issue=19|pages=23|access-date=2021-01-29|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206181350/https://books.google.com/books?id=LrgDAAAAMBAJ&q=cicely+tyson+miles+davis+jet+1968&pg=PA23|dead-url=no}}</ref>戴维斯在1967年的专辑《魔术师》中使用了泰森的一张照片。戴维斯在1967年告诉媒体，他打算在1968年3月和泰森离婚后再结婚，<ref>{{Cite journal|date=November 2, 1967|title=Miles Davis To Make March Merger With Cicely Tyson|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=K7gDAAAAMBAJ&q=cicely+tyson+miles+davis+jet&pg=PA56|journal=Jet|volume=33|issue=4|pages=56|access-date=2021-01-29|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206174229/https://books.google.com/books?id=K7gDAAAAMBAJ&q=cicely+tyson+miles+davis+jet&pg=PA56|dead-url=no}}</ref>但那年9月他和歌手贝蒂·戴维斯结婚了。<ref>{{Cite journal|date=October 17, 1968|title=One Of Sexiest Men Alive|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hTgDAAAAMBAJ&q=betty+davis+miles+davis+jet+1968&pg=PA48|journal=Jet|volume=35|issue=2|pages=48|access-date=2021-01-29|archive-date=2020-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200528035130/https://books.google.com/books?id=hTgDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA48&dq=betty+davis+miles+davis+jet+1968&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj6_d7Qz7nmAhXPWc0KHQfUC0wQ6AEwAHoECAIQAg|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

1978年，泰森和戴维斯重启两人的关系。1981年11月26日，由亚特兰大市长安德鲁·杨举行，两人在演员比尔·科斯比的家中举行了婚礼。<ref name=":0" />由于戴维斯脾气易怒和不忠，两人的婚姻非常混乱。<ref name=":0" />戴维斯认为泰森救了他的命，帮助他克服了可卡因成瘾。<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|title=Miles: The Autobiography|author1=Davis, Miles|author2=Troupe, Quincy|publisher=Simon & Schuster|year=1990|isbn=978-0-671-72582-2|url=https://archive.org/details/milesautobiograp0000davi}}</ref>他们住在加利福尼亚州[[马里布_(加利福尼亚州)|马里布]]和纽约市，直到1988年她提出离婚。<ref>{{Cite journal|date=1988-02-22|title=Cicely Tyson To Divorce Trumpeter Miles Davis|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gbsDAAAAMBAJ&q=cicely+tyson+miles+davis+jet&pg=PA13|journal=Jet|volume= 73| issue =  21|pages=13}}</ref>1989年，两人离婚，1991年，戴维斯去世。<ref name=":0" />

17岁时，泰森生了一个女儿。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/books/2021/01/26/cicely-tyson-book-life-career-just-as-i-am-memoir/6698395002/|work=USA Today|title=Cicely Tyson’s death comes days after her memoir was released. These are the book’s most poignant moments|first=Anika|last=Reed|date=2021-01-26|access-date=2021-01-29|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324160903/https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/books/2021/01/26/cicely-tyson-book-life-career-just-as-i-am-memoir/6698395002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>她是德尔塔西格玛西塔姐妹会的名誉成员。泰森是一名[[素食主義|素食主义者]]。<ref>Armstrong, David. (1991). ''The Great American Medicine Show''. Prentice Hall. p. 62. {{ISBN|978-0133640274}}</ref> 

2021年1月28日，泰森去世，享年96岁。<ref name = Variety>{{cite web |last1=Dagan |first1=Carmel |title=Cicely Tyson, Pioneering Hollywood Icon, Dies at 96 |url=https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/cicely-tyson-dead-dies-1234895188/ |website=Variety |access-date=2021-01-29 |language=en |date=2021-01-28 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129001714/https://variety.com/2020/tv/news/cicely-tyson-dead-dies-1234895188/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

